          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1605707770606-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1605707770606-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1605707770606-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil half a kettle</p><p>Add the <strong>dried cranberries </strong>to a bowl and cover them in <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chicken breasts</strong> to a chopping board and cover with a sheet of <strong>cling film</strong></p><p>Bash the<strong> chicken breasts</strong> with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> until evenly flattened – these are your<strong> chicken escalopes</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1605707787029-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1605707787029-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1605707787029-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1605707787029-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1605707787029-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a handful of <strong>flour</strong> to a plate with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Crack the <strong>egg<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</strong> </span>into a shallow bowl and beat with a fork</p><p>Add the <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> and <strong>dried sage </strong>to another plate</p><p>Coat the <strong>chicken escalopes</strong> in the <strong>flour</strong>, tap off the excess, then add them into the <strong>beaten egg<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>and finally press them into the <strong>breadcrumbs</strong> firmly to evenly coat all over</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1605707817690-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
