          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1605707817690-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is coated, add the<strong> bacon</strong> and <strong>Tenderstem broccoli</strong> to a baking tray (use <strong>tin foil</strong> to avoid mess!)</p><p>Drizzle the broccoli with a little <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and put the tray in the oven for 12-15 min or until the bacon is crispy and the broccoli is slightly charred</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4--1605707829754-x200.jpg",
